UserInput = GetInput("Enter Card Number")
SQLQuery = "SELECT * FROM Payments WHERE CardNumber = '" + UserInput + "';"
Result = Execute(SQLQuery)
This concatenates untrusted input, opening the door for injection.
Secure Example (Pseudocode)
UserInput = GetInput("Enter Card Number")
SQLQuery = "SELECT * FROM Payments WHERE CardNumber = ?"
Result = ExecuteWithParameters(SQLQuery, UserInput)
